<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٧]</span> أَبُو العُرْيانِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>اسْمُهُ أُنَيسٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قالهُ ابنُ عُلَيّةَ، عنْ خالدٍ الحَذّاءُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٨]</span> أَبُو العُرْيانِ المُجَاشِعيُّ، البَصْريُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عنِ ابنِ عبَّاسٍ، اسْمُهُ برَكةُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٨١٩]</span> أَبُو مُوسَى <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>اسْمُهُ إِسْرائيلُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عنِ الحُسَينِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>رَوى عنهُ ابنُ عُيَينةَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٨٢٠]</span> أَبُو عَمْرٍو النَدَبيُّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>اسْمُهُ بِشْرُ بنُ حَرْبٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٨٢١]</span> أَبُو أُمَامةَ بنُ سَهْلِ بنِ حُنَيفِ بنِ وَاهِبٍ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>اسْمُهُ أَسْعدُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
